data.title: 2020 Endorsement Slate for Harris County, Fort Bend County, Brazoria County, and Waller County

data.text: All Houston Business Connections Newspaper readers are strongly encouraged to cast their ballot for duly-qualified candidates who are endorsed on our slate. A few of our endorsed candidates in the Tuesday, November 3, 2020, general election are Kevin Brady, Johnny Teague, Wendell Champion, Troy Nehls, Sylvia Garcia, Brian Babin, Jeff Boyd, Staci Williams, Bert Richardson, Kevin Patrick Yeary, David Newell, Terry Adams, Fredericka Phillips, Jearalynn Manor, Nile Copeland, R.K. Sandill, Cheryl Elliott Thornton, Bruce Bain, Dawn Deshea Rogers, Te'iva Bell, Arlene Hecht, Julia Maldonado, Mary Nan Huffman, Lesley Briones, Genesis Draper, Bill Harmon, Christian Dashaun Menefee, Chris Daniel, Eric William Carter, Israel Garcia, and Mark Alan Harrison. Houston Business Connections Newspaper is published by Aubrey R. Taylor Communications. All Rights Reserved.
